div.p:
Mr. Eden then recapitulated the items agreed upon
                                for discussion by the Heads of States on the afternoon of July 19.
                                These were: 
                                    1.

Agreed text on political control of Germany;
                                    2.

Poland;
                                    3.

The German fleet and merchant marine;
                                    4.

Spain;
                                    5.

Implementation of the Yalta Declaration;
                                    6.

Yugoslavia;
                                    7.

Rumania.
